{"type": "article", "id": 4736, "title": "Plug & Feather 石面手表", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-26T08:00:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233545Hw2RkKfo5xtnIjJD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t来自加利福尼亚州圣塔莫尼卡的设计团队 Plug &amp; Feather 日前推出一款石面手表，表盘采用 100% 石头材质，且每一块表盘都是天然的石材纹路，这是自然的迷人之处，保证了每一块表盘都将是独一无二的。目前，Stone Face Watches 正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，提供宝蓝色的方钠石、云碧玉、紫硅碱钙石、雪花黑矅石、红玛瑙 5 种材质的表盘，现售价 109 美元（约合人民币 676 元），<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/900522017/plug-and-feather-stone-face-watches\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233542urZCGPLNDKRMawTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233543kbyoc1N2TY8sdwin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233543X91Zm8OMLfE3JQRz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233544dNmiyaJz4lERprXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233544jLKE2sDSim9dOR4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233544SXNB56CUQO7L29wx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}